(In the Maximal base)
Kenzo felt himself slowly regaining concenius.  He squinted his eyes
as the door to the CR opened and light flooded the pod.
"Where am I?" He asked wearily as he became familiar with his
surroundings.

OOC: Well I'm back.  Had some computer down time.  Last I read Kenzo
was put in the CR chamber of the Maxial base. 

(Front door of the Predicon base)
"No one notices Waspinator! Wazzzpinator just sit in front of base
blown to bits suffering and no one help!" Waspinator griped still
damaged from being blasted by Megatron Revived.

(Out side of whereever it was that Puppet Hydras and Vykos were meeting)
Inferno marched back in forth as if keeping gaurd, while on the other hand
"ZZzzzZZzzZZ" Quickstrike was fast asleep.
